{
  "stem": "26142.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they came back-- when we came back, we had already-- we were able to have bread for-- to bake bread for-- for-- for the holiday of Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How much time do we have?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Six minutes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my-- my sister-in-law, she-- she took to-- to-- to bake-- bake some-- some challah baked bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had apples.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had-- we made-- we prepared a meal for Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rosh Hashanah we saw-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This-- the-- the-- the man from the house, he said, he isn't going into.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is no-- no-- shul or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There isn't going out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He'll stay in the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when I looked out the window of the house, I saw catty corner the-- the-- third or fourth house down the street in the city, that there were people with white bands walking-- a lot of people into this-- this house.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I-- I talked to this man, you know, from the house, Berl Gefner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said they-- they probably have a minion there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They have a minion there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed all in this room-- Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then suddenly, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Manci and the children were in bed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were also laying-- laying down-- kind of-- what is there to do?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had one [NON-ENGLISH] that Moshe would look into it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother, Tsvi and I wouldn't even look into the [NON-ENGLISH] of the Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly, I see a truck stops in front of the house-- four soldiers-- German soldiers get off, and an officer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he comes into the-- to this room in our-- he opens up, comes in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he sees everybody is laying down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the German officer says, [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
